<plot>Smitty brought his nephew Joseph into the family business. Although he never wanted to be a mobster, Joseph loves his uncle and performs his job dutifully until he meets Mika. In Mika, he finds distraction and a strong incentive to defy his uncle and leave the business. Impatient and doubting his profession more than ever, Joseph wants out.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?346181</url></doc>
